casebody.data:
Haley R. TAYLOR
v.
Tatyana HOLDEN, et al. NO. 2018-CC-1365 Supreme Court of Louisiana. December 3, 2018 Granted. The judgment of the district court granting the motion to quash is reversed. Relator's motion to compel is granted. See La. Code Civ. P. art. 1422. WEIMER, J., would deny.
